{"content": "<p>Phases is a visual representation of realities that are out of phase. Interference patterns, colorful echoes, and emerging secrets are explored. Mathematical functions produce constant motion, but rarely, a peaceful scene resolves within the chaos.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t<h2>Phase Collection Overview</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>The Phase collection literally glows color as patterns dance like a square framed grid of LED lights might at a light show. There is something to the tightly spaces lines and waves of shifting patterns that affects the viewer. The distortion amongst the ordered square is palpable.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.artblocks.io/marketplace/asset/0xa7d8d9ef8d8ce8992df33d8b8cf4aebabd5bd270/143000663\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"752\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/loren-bednar-phase-1020x1024.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/loren-bednar-phase-1020x1024.png 1020w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/loren-bednar-phase-300x300.png 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/loren-bednar-phase-150x150.png 150w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/loren-bednar-phase-768x771.png 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/loren-bednar-phase-600x602.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/loren-bednar-phase-100x100.png 100w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/loren-bednar-phase.png 1034w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Phase 663 by Loren Bednar collected by MintFace</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t<h2>Phase Traits</h2>\t\t\n\t\t\t<h5>Resolution Trait</h5>\t\t\n\t\t<p>The collection revels in low resolution pixels with 'Resolution' trait giving you seven variants to choose from. 1024 x 1024 (160 artworks) is the highest resolution with 16 x 16 (150 artworks)  the lowest resolution. </p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"702\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/16x16-resolution.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/16x16-resolution.png 888w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/16x16-resolution-300x281.png 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/16x16-resolution-768x720.png 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/16x16-resolution-600x562.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Horizontal Scanlines trait variant</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t<h5>Scanlines</h5>\t\t\n\t\t<p>'Checkered', 'Horizontal' and 'Vertical' are the three 'Scanlines' variants with the latter two being the rarest variant. </p><p>'Checkered' does what you'd expect and adds a grid texture across the artwork. </p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"510\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/horizontal-scan-lines-loren-bednar-1024x697.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/horizontal-scan-lines-loren-bednar-1024x697.png 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/horizontal-scan-lines-loren-bednar-300x204.png 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/horizontal-scan-lines-loren-bednar-768x523.png 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/horizontal-scan-lines-loren-bednar-600x409.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/horizontal-scan-lines-loren-bednar.png 1222w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Horizontal Scanlines trait variant</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t<h5>Palette</h5>\t\t\n\t\t<p>There are a wide variety of palette options (34) in the collection. I tend to like the ones with teal / purple / pink evolutions like 'Interfere', 'Luminous', 'Enhance' and 'Delve.' They all feel like they're part of the same family.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"522\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/palette-traits-1024x714.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/palette-traits-1024x714.png 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/palette-traits-300x209.png 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/palette-traits-768x535.png 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/palette-traits-600x418.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/palette-traits.png 1182w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Interfere, Luminous, Enhance and Delve traits</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t<h2>21st August 2021 Release Date</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>The 2021 art bull market was in full swing by late August and the Phase collection got swept up in the fervour with some works such as Phase #445 with 'Enhance' Palette and 'Checkered' Scanlines selling for 14.89 eth. </p><p>You can pick up your pick of Phase artworks now for less than 0.3 eth.</p><p> </p>\t\t\n\t\t\t<h2>Displaying Phases</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Go big is the recommendation from Loren Bednar. The Phase collection is meant to be exhibited super sized so the low resolution on-chain pixels can bathe the viewer in light.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://oncyber.io/line541\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tLoren Bednar | Line 541\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>"}